author: Buddha
message: Do not overrate what you have received, nor envy others. He who envies others does not obtain peace of mind.
title: Thought of the day

author: Jessamyn West
message: It is very easy to forgive others their mistakes; it takes more grit to forgive them for having witnessed your own.
title: Thought of the day

author: Plato
message: Bodily exercise, when compulsory, does no harm to the body; but knowledge which is acquired under compulsion obtains no hold on the mind.
title: Thought of the day

author: Bruce Lee
message: Always be yourself, express yourself, have faith in yourself, do not go out and look for a successful personality and duplicate it.
title: Thought of the day
